<p> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">yasmin dṛ</lem><rdg wit="#B #L #N1 #D #U1">yasmiṃ</rdg></app>ṣṭe <app><lem wit="#ceteri">deśakasya</lem><rdg wit="#U1">darśakasya</rdg><rdg wit="#E">deśika°</rdg></app> trāso na bhavati/ tasya manaḥ śuddhaṃ bhavati/ <app><lem wit="#ceteri">yasya</lem><rdg wit="#U1">om.</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#P #L">pṛthivyāṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B #E #U2">pṛthvyāṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#D #N1 #N2">pṛthivī</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">pṛithīvī</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">kīrtir</lem><rdg wit="#E">vītir</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">kīrti</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">kītīr</rdg></app> bhavati/ yasya manomadhye <app><lem wit="#ceteri">satpuruṣavacanaviśvāso</lem><rdg wit="#N2">satpuruṣavacanaḥ viśvāso</rdg><rdg wit="#E">satpuruṣasya vaco viśvāso</rdg><rdg wit="#U1">vacanaviśvabhyāso</rdg></app> bhavati/ yo rājā <app><lem wit="#ceteri">sadānandapūrṇo</lem><rdg wit="#E">sadānaṃdarūpo</rdg><rdg wit="#L">sānaṃdapūrṇo</rdg></app> bhavati/ yasya pārśve pratyakṣam a<app><lem wit="#ceteri">nekaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B #L #E">aneka°</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#E">manohārivastūni</lem><rdg wit="#ceteri">manohārivastu</rdg></app> <app><lem resp="#ego" type="emendation">bhavanti</lem><rdg wit="#E">em. tiṣṭhaṃti</rdg><rdg wit="#ceteri">bhavati</rdg></app>/ etādṛśasya <app><lem wit="#ceteri">rājño</lem><rdg wit="#E">rājña</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#D #N1 #N2 #U1">'gre</lem><rdg wit="#B #P #U2">ye</rdg><rdg wit="#L">yad</rdg><rdg wit="#E">idaṃ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#ceteri">yogarahasyaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#B">thogarahasyaṃ</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#N1 #N2 #U1">karttavyaṃ</lem><rdg wit="#D">karttavya</rdg><rdg wit="#E #P">kathanīyam</rdg><rdg wit="#B #L">kathyaniyaṃ</rdg><rdg wit="#U2">kathyate</rdg></app>/ </p><lg> <tl><app><lem wit="#ceteri">na</lem><rdg wit="#B #L">ni</rdg></app> <app><lem wit="#E #P #U2">snehān na</lem><rdg wit="#ceteri">śnehān</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#E #P #U2"/><rdg wit="#B #L">nā</rdg><rdg wit="#D #N1 #N2">a</rdg></app><app><lem wit="#ceteri">bhayāl lo</lem><rdg wit="#E #U1">b